      "lineNbr": 204,
      "author": {
        "id": 1002970
      },
      "writtenOn": "2026-07-16T07:17:37Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Agreed, and fixed with startup-only gating.\nThe implementation now tracks whether a positive tach sample has been seen:\n\n- before first positive sample: ignore startup 0 RPM transient readings\n- after first positive sample: evaluate 0 RPM normally\n- on fan absence: reset startup gating state\n\nThis avoids boot false alarms without masking real 0 RPM failures.",
      "parentUuid": "d7c300d9_cd138f38",
      "revId": "6964af47cd5bb02acd36f27b19ffeabc2fe84bd7",
      "serverId": "adbd0a64-1f21-4d83-b585-671fe73cb6e4"
